[47.824225, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mThe search results from Expedia reveal three available Alaskan cruises departing on July 10, 2025, and returning on July 17, 2025:\r\n\r\n1. **Alaskan Glacier Adventure**:\r\n   - Cabin Type: Interior\r\n   - Price: $1200 per person\r\n   - Booking Status: Payment pending\r\n\r\n2. **Alaska Discovery Voyage**:\r\n   - Cabin Type: Oceanview\r\n   - Price: $1500 per person\r\n   - Booking Status: Payment pending\r\n\r\n3. **Journey to the Last Frontier**:\r\n   - Cabin Type: Balcony\r\n   - Price: $1800 per person\r\n   - Booking Status: Payment pending\r\n\r\nAll cruises are departing from Alaska and are currently available for booking.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[48.950505, "o", "\u001b[93mPlanner: User: Ask the user to choose one of the available Alaska cruise itineraries: \"Alaskan Glacier Adventure\" for $1200 per person, \"Alaska Discovery Voyage\" for $1500 per person, or \"Journey to the Last Frontier\" for $1800 per person.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
