[94.711, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mYour booking for the \"Alaska Discovery Voyage\" cruise has been successfully confirmed. Here are the details:\r\n\r\n- **Booking ID:** EXP123456789\r\n- **Cruise Name:** Alaska Discovery Voyage\r\n- **Departure Port:** Alaska\r\n- **Departure Date:** July 10, 2025\r\n- **Return Date:** July 17, 2025\r\n- **Cabin Type:** Oceanview\r\n\r\n**Passengers:**\r\n1. John Doe, Age: 34, Passport: X1234567Z\r\n2. Jane Doe, Age: 32, Passport: Y7654321X\r\n\r\n**Financials:**\r\n- **Total Cost:** $3500\r\n- **Payment Status:** Pending (payment to be completed via Expedia)\r\n\r\n**Contact Information:**\r\n- **Email:** johndoe@example.com\r\n- **Phone:** +1-800-555-0199\r\n\r\nPlease ensure the payment is completed to finalize the booking. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or need further assistance.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
