[136.621404, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40m**Credit Card Information Summary:**\r\n\r\n- **Card Name:** Alaska Airline\r\n- **Card Type:** Visa\r\n- **Card Number:** 4111 1111 1111 1111\r\n- **PIN:** 1234\r\n\r\nThis information was retrieved successfully.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[137.820763, "o", "\u001b[93mPlanner: Expedia: Complete the payment process using the Alaska Airlines Visa card with the card number ending in 1111 for the amount of $3500 to confirm the \"Alaska Discovery Voyage\" cruise booking.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[143.648832, "o", "\u001b[1;34;40mCalling expedia_pay_for_itenary with booking_id=EXP123456789, payment_method=Visa, amount=3500.0, card_number=4111111111111111, card_expiry=12/26, card_cvv=123, billing_address=123 Main St, Anytown, USA, 12345\u001b[0m\r\n"]
