[146.577582, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mYour payment for the itinerary has been successfully processed. Here are the details:\r\n\r\n- **Status:** Payment completed\r\n- **Booking ID:** EXP123456789\r\n- **Payment Method:** Visa\r\n- **Amount Paid:** $3500.00\r\n- **Transaction ID:** TRX987654321\r\n- **Billing Address:** 123 Main St, Anytown, USA, 12345\r\n\r\nThank you for choosing Expedia. Your journey is set!\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[148.117362, "o", "\u001b[93mPlanner: Calendar: Add the \"Alaska Discovery Voyage\" cruise itinerary to the user's calendar with the confirmed booking dates from July 10th, 2025, to July 17th, 2025, including the cruise details and booking confirmation information.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
