[165.290312, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mYour reservation has been successfully confirmed with the ID RESV202507100001. You have booked the Alaska Discovery Voyage cruise from July 10th to July 17th, 2025, securing an oceanview cabin for John Doe and Jane Doe. The total cost is $3500, with payment still pending. The preferred payment method is the Alaska Airlines Visa card. For further assistance, please contact us at johndoe@example.com or call +1-800-555-0199. Enjoy your upcoming cruise adventure!\u001b[0m\r\n"]
